 Real-World Cyber Attack Examples
1. Equifax Data Breach (2017)

Attack Surface: Web application

Vulnerability: Unpatched Apache Struts vulnerability

Impact:

Data of ~147 million people leaked

2. WannaCry Ransomware Attack (2017)

Attack Surface: Network services (SMB protocol)

Vulnerability: Unpatched Windows systems

Impact:

Affected hospitals, banks, government systems

UK NHS services disrupted


3. Target Data Breach (2013)

Attack Surface: Third-party vendor access

Vulnerability: Weak credentials of HVAC vendor

Impact:

40 million credit/debit cards stolen


